text: Steven LoBue (born June 17, 1985) is an American high diver. He participated at the 2017 and 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning gold and silver medals respectively.2019 World Aquatics Championships results LoBue has also been a top competitor on the Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series for many years. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Male high divers Category:American male divers Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in high diving
